        </div>
        <div class="fluid user__info">
          <h6>Michael Chen</h6>
          <p class="user__role">Travel Writer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card testimonial__card">
      <p class="quote">"As a creative writer, I appreciate how Blogify lets me focus on storytelling without
